### NFSIM-CHEM-06 — Ketone/BHB Monitor

**README.** Single-analyte β-hydroxybutyrate (BHB) meter. Ketogenic diet management, diabetic ketoacidosis screening.

**SPECIFICATIONS.** BHB dehydrogenase + NAD/NADH detection strip; range 0.1–8 mmol/L; ~$35.

**THEORY.** BHB + NAD⁺ → AcAc + NADH. NADH → e⁻ (via mediator) at WE.

**ASSEMBLY.** Same chassis family as CHEM-05.
